Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:03.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119641,123186}St. Tail, that's as far as you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:29.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145708,149087}You've done it, Inspector Kitamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:32.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149504,152548}-Thank you for your trouble.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:35.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154092,155927}That was just perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:41.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156177,161099}It's no good.\NThe real St. Tail is much faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:45.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162016,165019}No matter how many simulations\Nwe do, it's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:49.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165269,169774}I'd like the chance to meet the real\NSt. Tail as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:52.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170024,172485}I'll get her for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:56.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172694,176030}St. Tail, prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:03:02.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177281,182036}A STRONG FOE!\NCONFRONTING AN ELITE DETECTIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:07.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185456,187959}Doesn't Asuka Jr. seem a bit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:10.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188209,190461}Maybe his idol gave him\Nthe cold shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:12.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190712,192839}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:17.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193089,197719}Lately, St. Tail hasn't been\Nshowing herself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198261,200638}So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:23.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201347,203933}Still, he's really down, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:26.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204851,206644}Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:33.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210773,213443}I heard about it, Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:37.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213651,217822}The police department has put together\Na team to arrest St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:43.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220366,223870}Heard that your father's lending\Na hand in it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:47.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224120,227832}Don't bother me.\NIt isn't a big thing. Just routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:58.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235173,238801}Sawatari, what's the news?\NLet me in on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:04.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242388,244390}According to Takamiya…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:10.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244640,250521}…looks like the police have finally\Nput together a team to catch St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:13.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250772,253566}And they're bringing in\Na secret weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253816,256235}What's that supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:21.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256694,261574}It's a super detective, the first ever\Nfor the police department.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:25.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262408,265661}Well, just hold on to your horses\Nfor the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:29.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265912,269415}I'll be back with more fantastic news.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:32.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270792,272084}Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:44.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282178,284180}-Asuka Jr.!\N-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:46.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284430,286432}Don't let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:50.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286682,290144}No matter what kind of\Nsuper detective they bring in…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:52.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290394,292939}…he'd never be a match for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293523,295566}Obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296901,298069}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:13.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311874,313960}May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:17.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314210,317505}I'm surprised. Such a cute Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317713,319674}Is there something I can do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322927,325096}So you were in the art business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:29.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325930,329308}Yes, my wife and I travel worldwide…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:33.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329559,333312}…collecting all sorts of artwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:39.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334146,339026}-I'm sure you make a wonderful couple.\N-But my wife has fallen ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:41.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339819,341153}Angel's Smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:45.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341404,345700}To pay for my wife's medical expenses,\NI had to sell our works of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:49.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345950,349453}But only that statue of the angel…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:53.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349871,353291}…I had no intention of letting go\Nof Angel's Smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:56.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353541,356711}But the owner of the Parkside Museum\Ntricked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:57.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356961,357920}Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:01.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358588,361299}He was to borrow it\Nonly for the exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:05.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361549,365136}But before I knew it, he said\Nthat I had sold it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:07.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365636,367513}Can't something be done?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:13.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367763,373728}Nothing. Without me knowing, he made\Ndocuments saying I had sold it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373936,375146}That's horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:19.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375688,379066}Just one more time…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:25.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379775,385364}…I want to display the Angel's Smile\Nbeside my wife's pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:30.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385740,390494}I'm sure God will grant you\Nyour wish. I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:39.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394373,399295}Mr. Asakura's wife is\Nin quite bad health.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:43.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399545,403424}So there isn't much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404467,406260}I'm a bit worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:51.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406510,411140}According to my information,\Nthe police's secret weapon…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:52.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411390,412934}…is really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413392,415436}What's so super about this detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415686,417730}I don't know all the details…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:07:01.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417980,421901}…but this brilliant detective\Nhas solved many tough cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:08.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422443,428407}I see. But I'm gonna show that lady\Nthe Angel's Smile one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:12.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428616,432078}No matter the opponent,\NI can't run without a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:15.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432286,435581}That would tarnish St. Tail's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:28.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446384,448135}You're being a pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:32.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448427,452306}Oh, come on, just one. Pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:35.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452556,455017}Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:45.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458729,465027}"I'll be at the Parkside Museum tonight\Nto pick up Angel's Smile. -St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:49.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465611,469740}-It's a note from St. Tail!\N-Is it for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:55.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471158,475162}-So you're Asuka Jr.\N-And just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:59.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476330,479959}Metropolitan Police, special\Ninvestigations, Inspector Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480209,482586}I'm in charge of\Nthe St. Tail investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:06.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482837,486132}-You're the--\N-Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:21.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498310,501564}-You're joking. She's a detective?\N-That's neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:25.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501814,505943}Wow, the Metropolitan Police has\Na woman as its secret weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:28.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506193,508154}Kaede Kitamura, 26 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:32.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508362,512825}After graduating top of her class,\Nshe entered the police department.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:36.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513075,516746}A normal person would have stayed\Non that path to success.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:41.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516996,521000}She's gone out of her way\Nto take part in this St. Tail arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:49.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525087,529467}Five feet, six inches tall\Nand approximately 105 pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:55.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529717,535222}-What are her measurements?\N-I'd say it's about 34, 23, 34.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:59.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537016,539185}How disgusting can guys be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:03.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539810,543856}St. Tail may be sailing\Ninto rough waters with this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544106,545649}That's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:07.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545900,547651}I won't lose to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:17.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553407,557453}My Lord, please protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:21.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558329,561874}Ruby, pray for me too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:26.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564001,566545}Worried, aren't you? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:30.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566796,570549}But today's not a good day,\Nsince it'll probably be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:44.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580935,584230}St. Tail isn't stupid enough\Nto get caught with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:48.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:584814,588192}We'll have to see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:56.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594281,596325}Son, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596575,598285}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:07.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603457,607253}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:14.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612299,614051}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:17.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615594,617513}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619014,621642}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:37.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634947,637408}Seira, here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:42.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637658,642538}That woman detective, I heard\Nshe's going to use a special weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:44.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642746,644165}Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:48.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644790,648669}Don't worry, I know.\NI won't be reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:54.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651005,654675}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:09.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665978,669773}If St. Tail is gonna show up,\Nit'll be from the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:13.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670024,673819}She'll slip through their fingers,\Nso I'll get a head start.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:29.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685331,689668}With this, we can identify the\Nmovements of everyone in the museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:32.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689919,692254}Right. It uses an ultraviolet ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:36.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692504,696300}No matter her disguise,\Nshe can't hide her body temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:40.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696550,700763}I see. And that's this red dot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:45.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702014,705267}There's an invader\Nabove the exhibition room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:48.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707019,708979}Welcome, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:25.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:743722,745224}That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:28.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745474,748978}But St. Tail isn't so dumb as\Nto get caught with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:44.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762366,764076}Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:57.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772251,777131}This seems too easy. Is there really\Na secret weapon, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:58.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777464,778757}It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:04.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783387,784972}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786015,788392}…Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:12.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790394,792730}…Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:34.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811915,814084}Just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:42.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818380,822843}After making such a grand statement,\Nwhat's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:46.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823344,826388}Everything is going as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:04.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841528,844990}St. Tail is headed southwest\Non First Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:09.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846325,849995}What a cute little thing.\NShe doesn't even know it's bugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:14.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850204,854375}If we follow this light,\Nwe'll find out where her hideout is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:17.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855250,857878}Tonight is St. Tail's last caper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:23.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858379,863967}Let's see… Where's the hospital\Nthat she's supposed to be in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:28.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864218,868138}Hold it, St. Tail!\NHold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868764,870265}Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:33.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870474,873602}I was waiting for you!\NI'll be the one to arrest you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:36.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874019,876063}What a guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:54.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893038,894873}Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:15:00.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895707,900170}I'm definitely gonna be\Nthe one to arrest St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:10.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907469,910806}Inspector Kitamura,\NSt. Tail is about to land.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:14.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911014,914726}She's going to\Nthe Seika City Community Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914977,916270}Why a hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:21.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916520,921817}The answer is simple. Catch St. Tail\Nand we'll know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:28.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927448,928740}Head her off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:54.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951638,954766}After she steals, regardless\Nof how good she is…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:57.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955017,957019}…she'll let down her guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:59.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957269,959354}Come on over, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:02.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961273,962608}She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:06.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962816,966069}St. Tail, this is as far as you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:21.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979333,981460}You sure blundered this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:25.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981710,985464}If you didn't get in the way,\Nwe would have had St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:29.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985714,989218}Be quiet! St. Tail's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:31.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990302,991845}Darn! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992221,993722}Inspector Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:38.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993972,998310}Don't worry, I'll find her no matter\Nwhere she escapes to with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:44.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000062,1004274}That woman detective,\Nhow did she know my destination?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:54.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009571,1014701}That's it, run. The tougher\Nthe opponent, the better the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:23.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041520,1043939}- Darn it!\N-Just keep cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:27.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045691,1047943}Now she's a rat in a sack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:40.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055909,1060455}How does she know where I'm going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:48.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064585,1068964}It's a tracking device!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:55.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074386,1075929}Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:01.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078348,1081059}Ruby, where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:07.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083729,1087524}It's no good. I'm…\NIt's too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:10.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087899,1090235}What shall I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:13.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091403,1093655}No doubt about it. She's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:16.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093905,1096700}-Let's go in.\N-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:24.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099119,1104124}It's moving. The inner courtyard!\NNo, she's headed out of the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:28.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106668,1108962}This time, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:31.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110005,1111131}It's stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:35.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113091,1115010}That mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:41.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117929,1121642}Uncle, grant me my one and only wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:47.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121892,1127522}Leave the St. Tail investigation\Nin Asuka Jr.'s hands. Oh, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:49.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127773,1129232}I'm sorry to say this…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:53.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129483,1133278}…but by now that woman detective\Nhas probably caught her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:56.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134988,1136698}What do you want here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:19:01.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136948,1141662}Now I've got you cornered!\NYou're St. Tail, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:07.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145582,1147626}St. Tail, you're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:11.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148377,1151171}This is a bad joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:14.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152255,1154633}It's no use trying to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:38.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176363,1178198}Dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:44.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182619,1184496}Dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:48.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184705,1188458}It's definitely an angel\Nwho brought it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:57.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195924,1197926}Hey, Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:02.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198135,1202973}Heard that you're back in charge\Nof the St. Tail investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:06.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203223,1206435}Yep. The mayor came\Npersonally to ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:11.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206685,1211690}How disappointing. That woman\Ndetective, she had some real pizzazz.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:17.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211940,1217612}Looks like I'm the only one\Nwho can catch St. Tail after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:23.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220782,1223368}Asuka Jr., good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:27.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226163,1227831}Why the sudden attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:31.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228331,1231835}You're getting so big-headed\Nearly in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:34.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232085,1234838}Darn it! You're a real pest!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:37.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235088,1237215}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:42.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238133,1242262}Catch me if you can!
